classes

java.util.Map<K,V> classes
classes maps classes to sets of their subclasses (which have an entry in this space). This is a performance tweak, so matching to subclasses can be done quicker. This way there is no need to search all objects for classes which extend a template class. This map is updated after each write (if needed).
